{"tid":1165881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人分享下當初接受洗腎既心情","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T14:01:44.000Z","uid":125742,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"620bcbb2a71eb5fc6a8f0377d5d102c167ae7544","tid":1165881,"uid":125742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"小妹今年25歲，不幸遺傳死鬼老豆既腎病，由細睇住佢由開始洗腎洗到死為止。<br />\n<br />\n22歲去美國果年，發現有尿道炎，死咗番黎醫，點知中六合彩唔見我中，中咗呢個遺傳病，食咗保腎藥兩年，不段覆診不段擔心。<br />\n<br />\n腎指數不段幾十、幾十咁升......直至依加，去到四百零度，正常人只係一百以內，佢今次話我得番一至兩成腎功能，去到七百開始要做手術......<br />\n<br />\n我唔想接受同唔知到時會做d咩，成世人無行過運，中小學都有比人蝦過...... 仲未遇到真愛，亦都唔想<br />\n辜負人，我正一天煞孤星，唔知生存有咩意義，我又係香港焦土派，仲點對人生有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1217d21b693cfd8e9845700acba82e5b0abcd6b7","tid":1165881,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"洗血or洗肚？"},{"pid":"c1184d93dc2963165213c773e74e761cedf8398a","tid":1165881,"uid":125742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1217d21b693cfd8e9845700acba82e5b0abcd6b7","tid":1165881,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"洗血or洗肚？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"未洗 應該開肚 見過老豆個肚好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90cf40b4b0a4b9331839118fc47e090a42cb46d","tid":1165881,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"不<strong>斷</strong>"},{"pid":"55958c47218648d10d60d907eb4e8a632e0ee309","tid":1165881,"uid":244525,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"我有方法幫到你，有意請聯絡"},{"pid":"3ce123a594b465fdb69670d17120cbe7e146f948","tid":1165881,"uid":125742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b90cf40b4b0a4b9331839118fc47e090a42cb46d","tid":1165881,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:01:57.000Z","msg":